<h2 id='update-a-user-39-s-status'>Update a user&#39;s status</h2>
<p>Update a user&#39;s status</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Definition</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>PUT https://api.zoom.us/v2/users/<span class="o">{</span>userId<span class="o">}</span>/status
</code></pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Example Request</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>curl https://api.zoom.us/v2/users/<span class="o">{</span>userId<span class="o">}</span>/status <span class="se">\</span>
   <span class="nt">-d</span> <span class="s1">'{
    "action": "string"
}'</span>
</code></pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Example Response</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight plaintext"><code>204 No Content
</code></pre></div>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Path Arguments</th>
<th>&nbsp;</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>userId <strong>required</strong></td>
<td>The user ID or email address</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Body Arguments</th>
<th>&nbsp;</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>action <strong>required</strong></td>
<td>The action type<div class="enum"><code>activate</code> set users status to active<br/><code>deactivate</code> set users status to inactive<br/></div></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
